<div style="max-width:72rem;margin:1.5rem auto;padding:0 1rem 2rem 1rem;">
    <div style="padding:1.5rem;border:1px solid #dbe3ef;border-radius:1rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#eff6ff 0%,#f8fafc 100%);">
        <h1 style="margin:0 0 .75rem 0;color:#0f172a;">cssHolmes Test Suites</h1>
        <p style="margin:0;color:#334155;max-width:56rem;">
            cssHolmes now has two complementary reference pages: the legacy HTML5 markup suite and a modern XTF/XMF theme and widget suite.
            Use the first for baseline markup diagnostics and the second for XTF tokens, slots, widgets, admin-style cards, and export-oriented inspection work.
        </p>
        <p style="margin:.85rem 0 0 0;color:#475569;max-width:56rem;">
            On plain XOOPS installs without XTF manifests, cssHolmes still runs in a reduced generic mode for inspect, measure, HTML5, accessibility, layout, and widget HTML diagnostics.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(18rem,1fr));gap:1rem;margin-top:1rem;">
        <div style="padding:1.25rem;border:1px solid #dbe3ef;border-radius:1rem;background:#fff;">
            <h2 style="margin:.1rem 0 .6rem 0;color:#0f172a;">Legacy HTML5 Suite</h2>
            <p style="margin:0 0 1rem 0;color:#475569;">
                Original markup-oriented checks for links, forms, deprecated elements, and baseline HTML smells.
            </p>
            <p style="margin:0;">
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="<{$cssholmes_html5_testsuite_url}>">Open HTML5 Suite</a>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div style="padding:1.25rem;border:1px solid #dbe3ef;border-radius:1rem;background:#fff;">
            <h2 style="margin:.1rem 0 .6rem 0;color:#0f172a;">Modern XTF/XMF Suite</h2>
            <p style="margin:0 0 1rem 0;color:#475569;">
                Practical samples for tokens, slots, widgets, admin-style cards, accessibility hints, and export-friendly inspection.
            </p>
            <p style="margin:0;">
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="<{$cssholmes_xtf_testsuite_url}>">Open XTF/XMF Suite</a>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div style="padding:1.25rem;border:1px solid #dbe3ef;border-radius:1rem;background:#fff;">
            <h2 style="margin:.1rem 0 .6rem 0;color:#0f172a;">Admin Workbench</h2>
            <p style="margin:0 0 1rem 0;color:#475569;">
                Theme scans, widget scans, import review, patch drafts, preview/apply/rollback flow, and workbench history.
            </p>
            <p style="margin:0;">
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="<{$cssholmes_admin_url}>">Open Workbench</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
